From: Hernan <herchu@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 19 May 2026 15:25:57 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 14/15] flatland_plugins: register camera plugin source
 (project-specific)

Adds src/camera.cpp to the flatland_plugins_lib sources. OpenCV is
already linked via patch 0007, so this patch only registers the new
source file. The actual camera.{h,cpp} files are provided by the
OpenRobOps sim-flatland project and COPYed into place at image build
time.
---
 flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt b/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt
index 5790b0a..ae41f18 100644
--- a/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/flatland_plugins/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -63,6 +63,7 @@ add_library(flatland_plugins_lib SHARED
   src/model_tf_publisher.cpp
   src/update_timer.cpp
   src/battery.cpp
+  src/camera.cpp
   src/bumper.cpp
   src/tween.cpp
   src/bool_sensor.cpp
